m plain `lowrank_two_stage_residual` on the same input.","Use the exact pinned `K=16, EF=12, signum, LR=3.2e-3, AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` recipe for the first post-fix run so the round isolates the code repair."],"next_hypotheses":["If the repaired `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` runs cleanly and beats the current `K=16` point, run the same family at `K=24, EF=12` to test whether routing helps across the mid-K band.","If it runs cleanly but is clearly worse than the current `K=16` frontier point, retire this routed branch and return to a genuinely new architecture family next round.","If it still crashes under the fixed launcher, treat the remaining issue as trainer/runtime integration rather than architecture quality and inspect the distributed training path before further family search."],"primary_variable":"code_fix"}
